{
  "stem": "18960.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- very quietly to make sure that no neighbors, no-- nobody hears me or sees me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- it was only at night, I was doing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But later-- later already, a couple of days later, my mother was at night reaching over some-- some drinks and some food to us into the hideaway.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- there were-- I would say-- I would say at that time, uncles, great uncles, cousins.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of them were murdered in cold blood and buried in those woods surrounding Schodnica.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are in unmarked graves, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few weeks after the Ukrainian pogrom, they declared-- the Germans were already entrenched.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they declared Schodnica Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which means the whole Jewish population had to evacuate, whoever was still alive, and go either to Borislav, which is next town, or to the following towns.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Drohobycz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was still another town, Sambor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the survivors of that pogrom were-- were-- they-- they spread out on those three places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Borislav, Drohobycz, and Sambor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We chose to go to Drohobycz, being that we had a-- an uncle that was killed already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he had a big house in Drohobycz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went there, and we stayed in their house in Drohobycz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Could you tell me who-- what members of your family you are including?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, my father, my mother, my sister, and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we couldn't accommodate my grandmother because she lived with us all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went to-- to live with an aunt of ours, that she lived also in Drohobycz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name was Pearl Reich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she lived with her, and she stayed there with her till she was killed by the Nazis in her own bed at the age of 93.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
